title: 'Disable the saslauthd_read_shadow SELinux Boolean'

description: |-
    By default, the SELinux boolean <tt>saslauthd_read_shadow</tt> is disabled.
    If this setting is enabled, it should be disabled.
    <sebool-macro enable="false" sebool="saslauthd_read_shadow" />

